<p><span class="anchor" id="p67"></span>من قصاص أَو أرش<a href="#p67" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p68"></span>وَإِن سرى<a href="#p68" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
